---
const {
  imageSrc = '/img/what-are-AI-agents.png',
  imageAlt = 'Network of Binary Ideas AI agents collaborating'
} = Astro.props as {
  imageSrc?: string;
  imageAlt?: string;
};
---

<section class="relative w-full px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-20 py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col-reverse gap-10 md:flex-row md:items-center md:gap-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:w-[60%] text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold [font-family:'Segoe_UI_Symbol-Regular',Helvetica]">
        <span class="text-white">WHAT ARE </span>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,#2b7fff_0%,#ac46ff_50%,#f6329a_100%)]">
          AI AGENTS?
        </span>
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#d0d5db] [font-family:'Segoe_UI_Symbol-Regular',Helvetica]">
        <p>
          AI Agents are like hiring three employees who never sleep, never take breaks, and cost a fraction of the price.
        </p>
        <p>
          They're smart digital helpers that respond to customers, answer questions, and take real actions – all on their own. They work through chat, text, email, and even phone calls.
        </p>
        <p>Think of them as your:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-left">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,#3785ff_0%,#b020f5_100%)] text-white text-sm font-semibold">
              ✓
            </span>
            <span><strong>Front desk</strong> person who answers at 2 AM on Christmas</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,#3785ff_0%,#b020f5_100%)] text-white text-sm font-semibold">
              ✓
            </span>
            <span><strong>Sales team</strong> that replies in under 60 seconds, every time</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,#3785ff_0%,#b020f5_100%)] text-white text-sm font-semibold">
              ✓
            </span>
            <span><strong>Customer service rep</strong> who never gets frustrated or calls in sick</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>You shouldn't have to choose between serving customers and capturing new leads. AI Agents let you do both.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:w-[40%]">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-[#fffefe1a] bg-[#fffefe0d] backdrop-blur-sm">
        <img
          src={imageSrc}
          alt={imageAlt}
          loading="lazy"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

